      <article class="not-card not-card--included reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M5 3h14v18H5zM8 7h8M9 17h6"></path></svg></span><small>Included in service</small></div><h3>Inside oven</h3><p>The accessible oven interior, racks and trays are cleaned as part of the booked service.</p></article><article class="not-card not-card--included reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4zM12 4v16"></path></svg></span><small>Included in service</small></div><h3>Inside cabinets</h3><p>Empty and accessible cabinet and drawer interiors are cleaned as part of the booked service.</p></article><article class="not-card reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M6 3h12v18H6zM6 10h12"></path></svg></span><small>Optional extra</small></div><h3>Inside fridge</h3><p>Interior shelves, drawers and accessible surfaces can be added separately.</p></article><article class="not-card reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4zM12 4v16M4 12h16"></path></svg></span><small>Optional extra</small></div><h3>Interior windows</h3><p>Inside glass and accessible frames can be added when required.</p></article><article class="not-card reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M5 20V4h14v16M9 8h6M9 12h6"></path></svg></span><small>Optional extra</small></div><h3>Walls and blinds</h3><p>Targeted wall cleaning and wet wiping individual blind slats are quoted separately.</p></article><article class="not-card reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 18h16M6 18V9h12v9M8 9l1-4h6l1 4"></path></svg></span><small>Specialist service</small></div><h3>Carpet steam cleaning</h3><p>Available separately with a two-room minimum.</p></article><article class="not-card reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 18h16M6 18V7h12v11"></path></svg></span><small>Optional extra</small></div><h3>Balconies</h3><p>Accessible outdoor sweeping and surface wiping.</p></article><article class="not-card reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M12 3v18M3 12h18M5.5 5.5l13 13"></path></svg></span><small>Condition-based quote</small></div><h3>Heavy buildup</h3><p>Thick dust, grease, mould or long-term neglect needs additional time.</p></article><article class="not-card reveal"><div class="not-top"><span class="not-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 20h16M6 20V6h12v14M9 9h6"></path></svg></span><small>Different service</small></div><h3>Vacate cleaning</h3><p>Empty-property and inspection-focused tasks need End of Lease Cleaning.</p></article>
      </div><div class="not-foot reveal"><p>Oven and cabinet interiors are included. Need carpet steam cleaning, interior windows or another specialist task? Send us the property details before booking.</p><a class="text-link light-link" href="/contact">Ask our team <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></a></div></div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="service-plan"><div class="routine shell"><div class="routine-copy reveal"><div class="kicker">Plan the move-in window</div><h2>Clean after key collection and before delivery.</h2><p>Move-In Cleaning is a one-off service. Use the short empty-home window to clean storage, appliances and floors before boxes and furniture make those areas harder to reach.</p><div class="frequencies"><div class="frequency"><strong>Get the keys</strong><span>Confirm access and working utilities.</span></div><div class="frequency"><strong>Keep it empty</strong><span>Delay deliveries until the service is complete.</span></div><div class="frequency"><strong>Clean</strong><span>Oven and empty cabinet interiors are included.</span></div><div class="frequency"><strong>Unpack</strong><span>Wait for any steam-cleaned carpets to dry.</span></div></div><a class="button blue" href="/booking">Book before moving day <i><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></i></a></div><div class="routine-visual reveal">__ASTRO_IMAGE_2__<div class="routine-quote"><p>Clean first. Unpack once.</p><span>A fresher start in the new home</span></div></div></div></section>

    <section class="section soft" id="compare"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="kicker">Before moving day</div><h2>Use the empty-home window well.</h2></div><p>Plan the clean after key collection and before furniture delivery so storage, floors and everyday surfaces are easy to reach.</p></div><div class="compare-grid reveal"><article class="clean-option"><span class="option-label">Before the clean</span><h3>Keep rooms empty and utilities working.</h3><p>Clear access helps the team clean the places that become difficult to reach after unpacking.</p><ul><li>Arrange entry after collecting the keys</li><li>Keep electricity and hot water connected</li><li>Remove packaging and leftover rubbish</li><li>Delay furniture delivery until cleaning ends</li></ul><a class="text-link" href="/contact">Plan property access <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></a></article><article class="clean-option"><span class="option-label">Before you unpack</span><h3>Start with clean storage and appliances.</h3><p>The most useful move-in tasks are handled before food, clothes and household items fill the space.</p><ul><li>Oven interior is included</li><li>Empty cabinet interiors are included</li><li>Add carpet steam cleaning if needed</li><li>Allow treated carpets to dry fully</li></ul><a class="text-link" href="/booking">Book Move-In Cleaning <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></a></article></div></div></section>

    <section class="section" id="how"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="kicker">How it works</div><h2>Plan Move-In Cleaning in four clear steps.</h2></div><p>Use the short window after key collection and before furniture delivery.</p></div><div class="process-grid reveal"><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Book</div><h3>Confirm the access date</h3><p>Choose a cleaning window after the keys are available.</p></article><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Confirm</div><h3>Keep the property empty</h3><p>Delay deliveries and remove leftover rubbish or packaging.</p></article><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Clean</div><h3>We prepare the home</h3><p>The cleaner follows the agreed kitchen, bathroom, storage and floor scope.</p></article><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Check</div><h3>Unpack after completion</h3><p>Allow any steam-cleaned carpets to dry fully before use.</p></article></div></div></section>

    <section class="section support"><div class="support-panel shell reveal"><div class="support-copy"><span class="whatsapp"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M20 11.5a8 8 0 0 1-11.8 7L4 20l1.5-4A8 8 0 1 1 20 11.5Z"></path><path d="M8.5 9.5c1 2.2 2.1 3.3 4.3 4.3"></path></svg></span><div><h3>Unsure what your home needs?</h3><p>Send us a quick WhatsApp message with the home size, condition and preferred date.</p></div></div><a class="button blue" href="/contact#whatsapp">Ask on WhatsApp <i><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></i></a></div></section>

    <section class="section faq" id="faqs"><div class="faq-layout shell"><div class="faq-intro reveal"><div class="kicker">Move-In Cleaning FAQs</div><h2>Service questions, answered.</h2><p>The practical answers that help make the first visit simple.</p><a class="text-link" href="/faqs">Explore all FAQs <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></a></div><div class="faq-list reveal">
      <article class="faq-item open"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="true">Who is Move-In Cleaning for?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>It is for people preparing an empty property before furniture, boxes and household belongings arrive.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">When should it be completed?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>After key collection and before furniture delivery, while rooms and storage remain empty.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Are oven and cabinet interiors included?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Yes. The accessible oven interior and empty cabinet and drawer interiors are included.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Can I add carpet steam cleaning?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Yes. Request it in advance and allow approximately six to twelve hours for drying.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">How early should I book?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>One to two weeks is sensible, especially near month-end or when specialist extras are required.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">What should be ready before arrival?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Provide secure access, working utilities and an empty property without rubbish or packaging.</p></div></div></article>
      </div></div></section>

